==============================
How to setup and run verifyme
==============================

------------
Requirements
------------

[install] git (>= 2.7.4)
[install] node.js (>= 5.9.1)
[install] npm (>= 3.7.3)

git clone https://github.com/0ndorio/verify_me.git [PROJECT_PATH]

-----------------------
Development environment
-----------------------
Use the Makefiles in [PROJECT_PATH]{client, server, utility}
for actions like setup, build, run, watch ...

---------------------------
Non Development environment
---------------------------

#
# [Server] Setup
#

cd [PROJECT_PATH]/server
npm install --production

#
# [Server] Run
#

cd [PROJECTPATH]/server
make run